### **GEE Results**

The results of the selected *GEE* models are presented in this section, for analysis the estimation values, standard errors, Wald-Test and Confidence intervals for each selected covariate are represented. The table generated for each model can be viewed by selecting the desired model, the user can download the generated table to his computer with the name of the model defined by the user. The table will be in .csv format.
Note: To perform a new analysis, it is suggested to restart the application to proceed with all the steps explained in the previous sections.
